'''Renatasians''' were [[Human/Legends|human]] settlers from the [[Agriworld/Legends|agriworld]] of [[Renatasia III]], in the [[Renatasia system/Legends|Renatasia system]].

Renatasian nuns ran the [[Commission for the Preservation of the New Order/Legends|COMPNOR]] orphanage on [[Botajef/Legends|Botajef]] where [[Natasi Daala]] grew up.

